# Privacy Policy

**CMHelpline** ("we", "our", or "us") is a mobile application developed for citizens to call or register their day-to-day grievances with the **Government of Tripura, India**.

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the CMHelpline mobile app.

---

## Information Collection and Use

The app may collect and store certain information provided by the user for the sole purpose of grievance registration and resolution. This may include:

- Name
- Phone number
- Grievance details (text, category, etc.)
- Call logs (only if initiated through the app)

This information is **not shared with any third parties**, and is solely used for addressing public grievances by authorized departments of the Government of Tripura.

---

## Permissions

CMHelpline may request access to:

- **Phone/Call**: To allow users to make calls directly to the helpline number.
- **Internet**: To submit grievance data to the centralized server.
- **Location (optional)**: To help identify the location of a grievance if submitted by the user.

We do not access or use these permissions for any other purpose.

---

## Data Retention

User data submitted through the app is retained only as long as necessary to process and resolve the grievance. It is stored securely and handled in accordance with applicable government policies.

---

## Security

We value your trust in providing your personal information, and we are committed to using commercially acceptable means of protecting it. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

---

## Third-Party Services

CMHelpline does **not** use third-party analytics or advertising SDKs. All communications and data remain between the user and official government servers.

---

## Children's Privacy

CMHelpline does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of 13. If we discover such data has been provided, it will be deleted immediately.

---

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

This policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage users to review the privacy policy periodically.

---

